name: Kyle Carson
description: I am a Christian and Independent, successful, I am a very self-motivated individual, I am very courteous, kind and affectionate. I enjoy long walks, movies, soft music, and playfulness with the friends, as well as other open social activities. I like a good conversation on most any subject. In my spare time I enjoy going to the gym, music, studying the Bible, chatting and reading. I am not an alcoholic, I do NOT smoke.
